</div></div><div id="vid_19bb1774-969f-48a9-bd33-02049b92f59a" unselectable="on" style="display&#58;none;"></div></div></span><span></span><div><ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW179967723 BCX8" role="list" style="font-family&#58;verdana;margin&#58;0px;padding&#58;0px;overflow&#58;visible;cursor&#58;text;list-style-type&#58;disc;"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="8" data-list-defn-props="&#123;&quot;335552541&quot;&#58;1,&quot;335559685&quot;&#58;720,&quot;335559991&quot;&#58;360,&quot;469769226&quot;&#58;&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;&#58;[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;&#58;&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;&#58;&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;&#58;&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;&#125;" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1" role="listitem" class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW179967723 BCX8" style="margin&#58;0px 0px 0px 24px;padding&#58;0px;overflow&#58;visible;cursor&#58;text;clear&#58;both;direction&#58;ltr;display&#58;block;font-size&#58;11pt;font-family&#58;&quot;whitney book&quot;, &quot;whitney book_msfontservice&quot;, sans-serif;vertical-align&#58;baseline;"></li><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="8" data-list-defn-props="&#123;&quot;335552541&quot;&#58;1,&quot;335559685&quot;&#58;720,&quot;335559991&quot;&#58;360,&quot;469769226&quot;&#58;&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;&#58;[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;&#58;&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;&#58;&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;&#58;&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;&#125;" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1" role="listitem" class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW179967723 BCX8" style="margin&#58;0px 0px 0px 24px;padding&#58;0px;overflow&#58;visible;cursor&#58;text;clear&#58;both;direction&#58;ltr;display&#58;block;font-size&#58;11pt;font-family&#58;&quot;whitney book&quot;, &quot;whitney book_msfontservice&quot;, sans-serif;vertical-align&#58;baseline;"></li><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="8" data-list-defn-props="&#123;&quot;335552541&quot;&#58;1,&quot;335559685&quot;&#58;720,&quot;335559991&quot;&#58;360,&quot;469769226&quot;&#58;&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;&#58;[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;&#58;&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;&#58;&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;&#58;&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;&#125;" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1" role="listitem" class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW179967723 BCX8" style="margin&#58;0px 0px 0px 24px;padding&#58;0px;overflow&#58;visible;cursor&#58;text;clear&#58;both;direction&#58;ltr;display&#58;block;font-size&#58;11pt;font-family&#58;&quot;whitney book&quot;, &quot;whitney book_msfontservice&quot;, sans-serif;vertical-align&#58;baseline;"></li></ul><div></div><h5 class="ms-rteElement-Heading5"><span data-ccp-props="&#123;&#125;"><span data-ccp-props="&#123;&#125;">A virtual public hearing took place&#58; 08/20/2025 @ 5&#58;30 pm.<br></span></span></h5><ul style="list-style-type&#58;disc;"><li><h6 class="ms-rteElement-Heading6">Watch the hearing&#58; <a href="https&#58;//gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https&#58;//www.youtube.com/%40oprddirectorsoffice5783/streams&amp;data=05%7c02%7cjo.niehaus%40oprd.oregon.gov%7c2454a6893d6f4ccf767508ddcde7b71b%7caa3f6932fa7c47b4a0cea598cad161cf%7c0%7c0%7c638893117294726505%7cUnknown%7cTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7c0%7c%7c%7c&amp;sdata=0kLFGzAJJJMMkqH3MvNns2a2kJyMsg3MOPGy2jz/hDA%3D&amp;reserved=0">https&#58;//www.youtube.com/@oprddirectorsoffice5783/streams</a></h6></li></ul><h4 class="ms-rteElement-Heading4" style="font-family&#58;&quot;whitney book&quot;, &quot;whitney book_msfontservice&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style="color&#58;inherit;font-family&#58;inherit;font-size&#58;26px;">Public Comments Received&#58;</span></h4><p>No Comments Received 07/28/2025 - 08/04/2025<br></p><p>No Comments Received 08/04/2025 - 08/10/2025</p><p>No Comments Received